you say-what is heyokah
you say-How can we rub it out
you say-What about the city's demise
you say-Tell me how it all began

without this u will not get the booklet but u get to keep the boots. i know for a fact cause it happened to me. i found the words to post just incase someone uses this page and reads the post, everything before that is correct, if there r any other gaps i will try to update.</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="left"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="questmessage.asp?Guide=5">Post a Comment</A></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="quests.asp">Browse other quests</A></font></p></td></tr><tr><td width="100%" valign="top" align="center"><p style="text-indent: 0; line-height: 100%; word-spacing: 0; margin: 0"><font size="2" face="Tahoma"><A HREF="submitquest.asp">Submit a Quest Walkthrough</A></font></p></td></tr></div></center>
       
